            <div class="spine-content">
              <div class="spine-num">IV</div>
              <div class="spine-title">From Eyes to Live</div>
              <div class="spine-mark">SOON</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="book-open-content">
            <div class="open-cover placeholder">
              <div class="ph-num">IV</div>
              <div class="ph-text">Cover · Coming</div>
            </div>
            <div class="open-details">
              <div class="open-numeral">IV</div>
              <div class="open-meta">
                <span>Volume IV</span>
                <span>In progress</span>
                <span>ETA TBD</span>
              </div>
              <h2 class="open-title">From Eyes to Live</h2>
              <p class="open-subtitle">The brain works. The Board approves. Now the question.</p>
              <p class="open-pull">"Can any of it survive real money?"</p>
              <p class="open-desc">Volume IV will document the next chapter — taking the supervised brain to live capital, measuring what's real, killing what isn't.</p>
              <div class="v3-state">⌛ Cover &amp; release date pending</div>
              <div class="open-ctas">
                <a class="book-btn book-btn-secondary"
                   href="https://t.me/+di3JKEUHYvQ5NDM0"
                   target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  📡 Notify me on Telegram
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

